=head1 TEST PROCEDURE

=begin html
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<PRE>
  RUT     MN0
   |       |
   |      MN0X
   |       |
   | <---- | BU (A=1&H=1&L=1) w/ HaO
